# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# EventFlow Edge Functions - Environment Variables
# Copy this file and set in Supabase Dashboard > Project Settings > Edge Functions
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# REQUIRED: Encryption key for credentials (32+ characters)
ENCRYPTION_KEY=your-32-character-encryption-key-here

# REQUIRED: Production origin for CORS
# Set this to your production domain (e.g., https://eventflow.example.com)
ALLOWED_ORIGIN=https://your-production-domain.com

# REQUIRED: Environment setting
# Set to 'development' to allow localhost:5173, 'production' for strict CORS
ENVIRONMENT=production

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Notes:
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# 1. ALLOWED_ORIGIN - Must be set for production! Without this, all requests
#    will be rejected with 403 CORS error.
#
# 2. ENVIRONMENT - Set to 'development' only in dev/staging environments.
#    In production, this should always be 'production'.
#
# 3. ENCRYPTION_KEY - Used for AES-GCM encryption of API credentials stored
#    in the database. Must be at least 16 characters (32 recommended).
#
# 4. Rate Limiting - Rate limits are applied per organization/user:
#    - WhatsApp: 30 messages/minute per organization
#    - AI Chat: 20 requests/minute per user
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
